sults.  \n  \n```  \n// C4319.cpp  \n// compile with: cl /W4 C4319.cpp  \nint main() {  \n   unsigned long a = 0;  \n   unsigned long long q = 42;  \n   q = q & ~(a - 1);    // C4319 expected  \n}  \n```"}